<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.4">
<l>kaṇamaruvu mayilakavu kaṭipōḻilcūḻ neṭumaṟukil</l>
<l>tiṇamaruvu kaṉamatiḷcūḻ tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>maṇamaruvu tōḷāycci yārkkappō yuralōṭum</l>
<l>puṇarmaruta miṟanaṭantāṟ kiḻantēṉeṉ poṉvaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my gold bangles to the one who walked so to break</l>
<l rend="indent">entwined marutu trees,</l>
<l>Having gone [there] with a mortar when a herdess,</l>
<l rend="indent">with fragrance-encircled shoulders, bound [him],</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by stout encircling thick walls</l>
<l>On long lanes surrounded by scented groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where flock-encircled peacock’s call.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
